com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Class DocumentPropertyValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.PropertyValue
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.SimplePropertyValue
        • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.DocumentPropertyValue

  • public final class DocumentPropertyValue
extends SimplePropertyValue
    A SimplePropertyValue that represents a binary document in the Analysis Repository.

    The value must conform to the "string" XML data type, and take the form documentId:fileSizeInBytes:fileName, where:

    • documentId is the identifier returned by the upload servlet when the document was uploaded
    • fileSizeInBytes is exactly as was specified to the upload servlet
    • fileName is exactly as was specified to the upload servlet
    Since:
    4.0
